name: roytang
text:
@ekafyi Oh no, a quiz! Lol I mostly know the local names, so gonna do some rough translation:

Image #1: On the board - garlic bread, sausages, biscuits, queso de bola (edam cheese), potato chips + various dips

Image #2:

Left dish: pancit bihon (chinese rice noodles?)

Right dish:
top - cuapaw ("Gua Bao" / pork belly buns)
top left - pork siomai (chinese dumpling)
bottom left - shrimp dumplings
bottom right - fried squid balls
top left - shrimp tempura
center - kikiam (ngoh hiang)
